data.description: Located in the quiet and peaceful neighborhood of Summer Lakes, this 3 bedroom, 2 1/2 bathroom, 2 car garage, 2-story pool home is move-in ready and needs minor touches to make it your own! The home features stainless steel appliances, high ceilings, a loft which overlooks the living room that could easily be converted into a fourth bedroom if needed, a master bedroom which is downstairs, new hurricane rated windows and doors and a beautiful pool and deck area which overlooks a pond. As soon as you walk through the door, it is open, bright, and feels like home. The property is located on a dead-end street so there’s no through traffic and is centrally located near Rowan Road and State Road 54, which offers quick access to US 19, all of the area beaches, and shopping centers. Pool homes in this area don’t last long so schedule your showing today!
